name: Codi Vore
description:
I saw there was a TI of Codi but thought I'd give a LoRA a shot anyway and have got some pretty good results so far, it obvious leans towards nsfw, so put that in the negative prompt if you don't want that. Have Fun!


Trained with 40 pictures.
Best results with weight: 0.7-1.
Trigger Words : cvv2 (not necessary but you can add it to add strength)

If anyone has any suggestions for LoRA, let me know and maybe I'll give them a go :)
